%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132559%2FGBeFULQa8AAWOvF.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20massive%20protest%20led%20by%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Saturday%20(December%2016)%20protested%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20being%20the%20given%20the%20project%20to%20redevelop%20the%20Dharavi%20slum%20area.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fremove-adani-save-dharavi-protesters-stage-massive-march-against-redevelopment-project%2Farticle67645451.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20were%20present%20and%20marched%20towards%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20the%20city%20from%20the%20slum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlogans%20like%20%E2%80%9CRemove%20Adani%2C%20Save%20Dharavi%E2%80%9D%20were%20visible%20on%20their%20posters.%20Protesters%20have%20demanded%20that%20all%20Dharavi%20residents%20be%20given%20500%20square%20foot%20home%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20led%20the%20march%2C%20said%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20falsely%20claiming%20that%20the%20tender%20for%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20(DRP)%20was%20issued%20during%20his%20chief%20ministership%2C%20while%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20government%20was%20in%20power.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20toppled%20the%20MVA%20government%20just%20so%20this%20project%20could%20be%20awarded%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20385px)%2085vw%2C%20385px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132638%2FGBeAUlPb0AAppmV.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22385%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132638%2FGBeAUlPb0AAppmV.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132638%2FGBeAUlPb0AAppmV-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132638%2FGBeAUlPb0AAppmV-683x1024.jpeg%20683w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22578%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20protest%20on%20Saturday.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40ShivSenaUBT_%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Dharavi%20residents%20but%20police%2C%20sanitary%20workers%20and%20mill%20workers%20should%20also%20get%20houses%20in%20Dharavi.%20I%20am%20not%20against%20development%20but%20this%20is%20the%20biggest%20TDR%20%5BTransfer%20of%20Development%20Rights%5D%20scam%20of%20the%20world.%20Adani%20is%20getting%20TDR%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20which%20means%20his%20next%20generations%20can%20also%20live%20peacefully%20without%20working.%20So%20much%20is%20the%20TDR%20that%20the%20government%20is%20gifting%20them.%20But%20we%20will%20not%20let%20that%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fuddhav-dharavi-project-biggest-tdr-scam-9071129%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20to%20redevelop%20Dharavi%20was%20taken%20in%202018%2C%20when%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Therefore%2C%20this%20sin%20is%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Fadnavis%20is%20currently%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20one%20can%20understand%20who%20financed%20the%20toppling%20of%20my%20government.%20With%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20around%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20help%20its%20friends%3B%20so%20my%20party%20was%20broken%20and%20its%20symbol%20was%20stolen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Dharavi%20MLA%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20was%20also%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%20have%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20MVA%20government%20that%20had%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Dharavi%20project%20was%20awarded%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20through%20a%20fair%2C%20open%2C%20internationally%20competitive%20bidding%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20tender%20conditions%20were%20finalised%20during%20the%20MVA%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20and%20have%20remained%20unchanged%20post-awarding.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20inaccurate%20to%20claim%20any%20special%20privileges%20granted%20to%20the%20awardee%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702800641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17132559%2FGBeFULQa8AAWOvF.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flarge-protest-in-mumbai-against-dharavi-redevelopment-project-given-to-adani-group%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20conglomerate%20says%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%20signed%20the%20agreement%2C%20but%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20denied%20this%20and%20said%20it%20was%20signed%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20before%20him%2C%20BJP's%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flarge-protest-in-mumbai-against-dharavi-redevelopment-project-given-to-adani-group%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20opens%20up%20on%20how%20she%20tackles%20anxiety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702800263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106061212%2Cimgsize-122373.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ft