n%20sell%20at%20prices%20far%20more%20than%20the%20original%20tag.%20Among%20the%20ones%20in%20great%20demand%20are%20very%20rare%20LPs%20and%20singles%20of%20%E2%80%98beat%20groups%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20garage%20bands%20which%20emerged%20in%20India%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20%E2%80%9970s%2C%20playing%20western%20pop%20and%20rock%20music.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20cut%20a%20few%20discs%20of%20their%20original%20compositions%20and%20cover%20songs%20of%20well%20known%20international%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20began%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20sounds%20of%20the%20Beatles%2C%20and%20then%20other%20bands%2C%20heard%20on%20the%20distant%20airwaves%20of%20Voice%20of%20America%20and%20the%20closer%20home%2C%20from%20Radio%20Ceylon%2C%20prompted%20young%20men%20to%20come%20together%20and%20set%20up%20similar%20beat%20groups..%20The%20Trojans%20from%20Bangalore%2C%20the%20Jets%20from%20Bombay%20and%20the%20Flintstones%20from%20Calcutta%20were%20among%20the%20earliest%20to%20be%20formed.%20Their%20equipment%20was%20rudimentary%20%E2%80%93%20some%20used%20homemade%20guitars%20and%20loud%20PA%20amplifiers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20handicap%20of%20not%20freely%20getting%20records%20to%20learn%20the%20chords%20and%20words%2C%20but%20their%20enthusiasm%20was%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201964%2C%20The%20Savages%20were%20formed%20in%20Bombay%20by%20drummer%20Bashir%20Sheikh%2C%20along%20with%20Russel%20Pereira%2C%20Hemant%20Rao%2C%20Prabhakar%20Mundkur%20and%20Ralph%20Pais.%20They%20started%20playing%20the%20live%20music%20circuit%2C%20notably%20at%20night%20clubs%20and%20discos%20like%20Trinca%E2%80%99s%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20at%20colleges%20and%20dances%20in%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pop%20music%20scene%20was%20picking%20up%2C%20and%20a%20new%20generation%20began%20grooving%20at%20these%20sounds%2C%20which%20were%20so%20different%20from%20what%20their%20parents%20had%20heard.%20%3Cem%3EJS%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3EJunior%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E)%20magazine%20was%20a%20must%20read%20and%20wearing%20batik%20shirts%20and%20bell-bottoms%20they%20thronged%20to%20music%20competition%20such%20as%20the%20Simla%20Beat%20Contest%2C%20sponsored%20by%20a%20cigarette%20company%2C%20which%20the%20Savages%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20bands%20played%20cover%20songs%2C%20with%20the%20occasional%20original%20number.%20What%20set%20the%20Savages%20apart%20is%20that%20they%20played%20many%20of%20their%20original%20compositions.%20They%20also%20made%20two%20LPs%20and%20many%20singles.%20One%207%E2%80%9D%20single%20featured%20two%20original%20songs%20by%20Hemant%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20%E2%80%98Pain%E2%80%99%20featuring%20budding%20jazz%20singer%20Asha%20Puthli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnusually%2C%20because%20recording%20companies%20were%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20in%20Indian%20bands%2C%20they%20also%20made%20two%20LPs%20(Long%20Playing)%20with%20Polydor%20Records%20India%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Live%E2%80%99%2C%20with%2011%20classic%20tracks%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98Black%20Scorpio%E2%80%99.%20They%20sold%20modestly%20at%20the%20time%20but%20have%20become%20collectors%E2%80%99%20items%20now%2C%20retailing%20online%20for%20up%20to%20500%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Free%20School%20Records%2C%20formed%20by%20two%20record%20collectors%20from%20Kolkata%20%E2%80%94%20Aveek%20Chatterjee%20and%20Rajeev%20Pandey%20%E2%80%94%20have%20reissued%20the%20LP%20%E2%80%98Live%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20limited%20edition%20of%20250%20on%20vinyl.%20Their%20day%20jobs%20are%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20but%20their%20spare%20time%20goes%20in%20republishing%20records%20by%20Indian%20and%20other%20musicians%2C%20old%20and%20new%2C%20of%20which%20they%20have%20already%20issued%20five%20LPs%20on%20vinyl%20and%20one%20on%20CD%2C%20since%202021.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%2C%20200%20copies%20of%20Train%20to%20Calcutta%20by%20folk%20singer%20Susmit%20Bose%2C%20were%20sold%20out%20within%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123906%2FAveek-and-Rajiv_FSSR.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123906%2FAveek-and-Rajiv_FSSR.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123906%2FAveek-and-Rajiv_FSSR-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689523%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAveek%20Chatterjee%20and%20Rajeev%20Pandey.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20new%20project%20involves%20getting%20permission%20from%20not%20just%20the%20bands%20but%20also%20from%20the%20recording%20company%2C%20the%20audio%20mastering%2C%20and%20working%20with%20the%20pressing%20plant%20in%20Europe.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20now%2C%20we%20have%20it%20down%20to%20a%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20say.%20Sen%20does%20the%20due%20diligence%2C%20tracking%20down%20rights%20owners%2C%20the%20bands%20and%20getting%20their%20go%20ahead%2C%20while%20Pandey%20manages%20the%20technical%20side%20and%20even%20does%20the%20art%20work.%20The%20whole%20process%20takes%20up%20to%20six%20months%20and%20both%20invest%20their%20own%20funds%20into%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20latest%20LP%2C%20the%20duo%20plans%20to%20publish%20more%20records%2C%20starting%20with%20one%20by%20the%20Indian%20band%20Parikrama.%20They%20think%20they%20are%20not%20just%20filling%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%2C%20because%20the%20bigger%20music%20companies%20completely%20ignore%20this%20segment%2C%20but%20also%20bringing%20out%20good%20music%20for%20a%20new%20demographic%20and%20for%20those%20who%20remember%20those%20bands%20from%20when%20they%20were%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702796991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17123743%2FSavages-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fto-bring-nostalgia-to-your-turntable-two-music-buffs-produce-re-mastered-vinyl-of-old-bands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Savages%20Live%2C%20a%20rare%20and%20expensive%20LP%2C%20is%20their%20latest%20release%2C%20aimed%20at%20collectors%20and%20newbies%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fto-bring-nostalgia-to-your-turntable-two-music-buffs-produce-re-mastered-vinyl-of-old-bands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20the%20deets%20on%20Aquaman%20and%20the%20Lost%20Kingdom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702796914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106060273%2Cimgsize-17648.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Faquaman-and-the-lost-kingdom-release-date-projected-budget-and-box-office-prospects-of-the-jason-momoa-starrer%2Farticleshow%2F106060300.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106060300.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMarked%20as%20one%20of%20the%20DCEU's%20most%20financially%20ambitious%20endeavors%2C%20%26quot%3BAquaman%20and%20the%20Lost%20Kingdom%26quot%3B%20carries%20a%20hefty%20%24215%20million%20budget.%20Achieving%20financial%20success%20hinges%20on%20the%20film%20exceeding%20%24400%20million%20in%20global%20box%20office%20earnings.%20The%20film%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20outperforming%20its%20predecessor%20and%20garnering%20international%20acclaim%20to%20offset%20its%20substantial%20production%20costs%20effectively.%20The%20spotl