%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d54fb50edbc52a865079b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20inside%20the%20VR%20goggles%20that%20the%20mice%20were%20wearing%20sometimes%20featured%20predators%20like%20owls.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Dombeck%2C%20Department%20of%20Neurobiology%20at%20Northwestern%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20from%20Northwestern%20University%20made%20virtual%20reality%20goggles%20for%20lab%20mice%20to%20wear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20mice%20are%20being%20studied%20to%20identify%20the%20neurons%20in%20the%20brain%20that%20form%20memories.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20data%20may%20help%20researchers%20understand%20human%20memory%20and%20how%20degenerative%20disease%20changes%20the%20brain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fillegal-lab-found-full-of-bioengineered-mice-and-infectious-diseases-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELab%20mice%3C%2Fa%3E%20strapped%20in%20to%20mini%20virtual%20reality%20goggles%20are%20roaming%20through%20digital%20mazes%20in%20the%20latest%20breakthrough%20in%20neurobiology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20teach%20us%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfographic-how-memory-works-2012-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20memory%20works%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20researchers%20at%20Northwestern%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20identifying%20the%20neurons%20in%20the%20brain%20that%20form%20memories%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20led%20by%20Daniel%20Dombeck%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20university's%20department%20of%20neurobiology%2C%20created%20miniature%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-used-metas-virtual-reality-headset-in-office-in-metaverse-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVR%20goggles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20place%20on%20lab%20mice%20to%20study%20how%20they%20remember%20navigational%20cues%20when%20traversing%20digital%20mazes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20advanced%20instruments%20to%20image%20brain%20activity%20are%20large%2C%20table-top%20devices%20that%20cannot%20be%20carried%20around%20on%20a%20mouse's%20head%20as%20they%20move%20through%20the%20environment.%20So%20instead%2C%20we%20hold%20the%20mouse's%20head%20still%20under%20the%20large%20microscopes%20(so%20we%20can%20study%20their%20brains)%2C%20and%20we%20let%20them%20run%20on%20a%20treadmill%20mounted%20under%20their%20limbs%2C%26quot%3B%20Dombeck%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20movements%20of%20the%20treadmill%20move%20the%20animal%20through%20a%20virtual%20world%20displayed%20in%20the%20goggles%2C%20complete%20with%20twisting%20mazes%20and%20depictions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-get-rid-of-mice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredators%20like%20owls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20set-up%2C%20we%20can%20then%20use%20our%20cutting-edge%20microscope%20systems%20to%20study%20brain%20activity%20during%20navigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dombeck%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20identify%20the%20exact%20neurons%20in%20the%20brain%20that%20are%20forming%20memories%20of%20the%20mazes%2C%20and%20in%20those%20neurons%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20identify%20which%20synapses%20are%20being%20modified%20to%20form%20the%20memories%20and%20through%20what%20mechanisms%20those%20synapses%20are%20modified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMouse%20research%20with%20human%20applications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnswering%20these%20questions%20with%20mouse%20brains%20will%20eventually%20help%20researchers%20understand%20how%20human%20brains%20know%20where%20we%20are%20in%20the%20world%20around%20us%2C%20how%20we%20form%20memories%20of%20our%20experiences%20and%20imagine%20solutions%20to%20our%20problems%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20how%20our%20memories%20degrade%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepper-bio-pitch-deck-ai-biotech-seed-round-2023-12%23pepper-bio-says-it-wants-to-help-find-treatments-for-untreatable-diseases-from-cancers-to-neurodegenerative-conditions-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneurodegenerative%20diseases%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20virtual%20environments%20enable%20researchers%20to%20use%20the%20most%20advanced%20recording%20instruments%20to%20study%20these%20questions.%20Future%20studies%20will%20include%20even%20smaller%20goggles%20so%20that%20mice%20can%20carry%20them%20around%20and%20run%20through%20virtual%20mazes%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20earliest%20studies%2C%20researchers%20showed%20the%20mice%20simple%20mazes%20depicted%20as%20long%20hallways%20with%20a%20reward%20hidden%20along%20the%20way.%20In%20a%20few%20cases%2C%20they%20added%20a%20looming%20stimulation%20like%20a%20predator%20hunting%20the%20mice%20from%20the%20virtual%20%26quot%3Bsky%26quot%3B%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20stimulation%20in%20real%20environments%20causes%20mice%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Ffight-flight-freeze-fawn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreeze%20or%20flee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reactions%20they%20have%20to%20survive%20a%20predatory%20bird%20attack%20in%20the%20wild%2C%26quot%3B%20Dombeck%20said.%20%26quot%3BMice%20reacted%20the%20same%20way%20in%20our%20VR%20goggle%20system%20as%20mice%20do%20in%20real%20environments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20studying%20how%20the%20navigation%20systems%20in%20the%20brain%20reacted%20to%20a%20looming%20stimulus%2C%20the%20neurobiologists%20found%20that%2C%20when%20the%20mice%20were%20freezing%20in%20place%20after%20seeing%20the%20virtual%20predator%2C%20the%20navigation%20neurons%20were%20reading%20out%20a%20different%20location%20from%20where%20the%20mice%20actually%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20as%20if%20they%20were%20thinking%20about%20where%20they%20would%20rather%20be%20%E2%80%94%20a%20safe%20covered%20location%20up%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%20where%20they%20were%20freezing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dombeck%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20excited%20about%20these%20results%20and%20will%20follow%20up%20more%20on%20this%20since%20they%20might%20help%20explain%20how%20imagination%20emerges%20in%20the%20brain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-made-mice-virtual-reality-goggles-study-memory-brain-study-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702795255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d56807a3c8094d5ddcbbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-made-mice-virtual-reality-goggles-study-memory-brain-study-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20from%20Northwestern%20University%20made%20virtual%20reality%20goggles%20for%20lab%20mice%20to%20identify%20the%20neurons%20in%20the%20brain%20that%20form%20memories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-made-mice-virtual-reality-goggles-study-memory-brain-study-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20inaugurates%20new%20terminal%20at%20Surat%20airport%2C%20Diamond%20Bourse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702795171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106059303%2Cimgsize-136648.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fgujarat-pm-narendra-modi-inaugurates-new-terminal-building-at-surat-airport-diamond-bourse%2Farticleshow%2F106059165.cms