4.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fncts-taeyong-drops-subtle-clues-about-potential-military-enlistment-schedule%2Farticleshow%2F106059402.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106059402.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENCT's%20Taeyong%20sparked%20speculation%20about%20impending%20military%20enlistment%20during%20recent%20concert.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Parliament%20Breach%20Accused%20Destroyed%20Key%20Evidence%20At%20Rajasthan%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20four%20persons%20were%20arrested%20for%20the%20shocking%20breach%20in%20Parliament%20security%20last%20Wednesday%2C%20one%20of%20their%20associates%20was%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Nagaur%20to%20destroy%20critical%20evidence%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20investigation%20has%20found%20that%20Lalit%20Jha%2C%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20reached%20Rajasthan's%20Nagaur%20-%20about%20450%20km%20from%20Delhi%20-%20after%20the%20incident.%20There%2C%20he%20met%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20who%20lodged%20him%20at%20a%20small%20hotel%20in%20Trishangaya%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20December%2013%2C%20when%20the%20security%20breach%20took%20place%2C%20Lalit%20and%20Mahesh%20approached%20a%20fire%2C%20apparently%20to%20get%20some%20relief%20from%20the%20biting%20cold.%20They%20then%20threw%20the%20phones%20of%20the%20four%20Parliament%20trespassers%20into%20the%20flames%2C%20destroying%20key%20evidence.%20Lalit%20had%20reportedly%20collected%20the%20phones%20of%20the%20four%20trespassers%20before%20the%20incident.%20He%20also%20allegedly%20shot%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20sent%20them%20to%20an%20acquaintance%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20seeking%20media%20coverage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20now%20found%20burnt%20parts%20of%20the%20phones%20from%20near%20the%20hotel.%20Mahesh%20and%20Lalit%20are%20among%20six%20people%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhanwar%20Lal%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20said%20it%20was%20only%20when%20police%20came%20to%20him%20that%20he%20realised%20how%20his%20hotel%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20incident%20that%20shocked%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20by%20his%20name%2C%20but%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20other%20information%20about%20him.%20Police%20took%20with%20them%20burnt%20parts%20(of%20phones)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20what%20the%20accused%20had%20done%20when%20they%20came%20to%20his%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20yet%20to%20recover%20the%20phone%20of%20Lalit%20Jha%2C%20who%20reportedly%20returned%20to%20Delhi%20after%20destroying%20the%20phones%20and%20was%20arrested%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20massive%20security%20breach%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20attack%20on%20Parliament%2C%20two%20intruders%20--%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%20--%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery.%20They%20then%20went%20from%20desk%20to%20desk%20and%20deployed%20coloured%20smoke%20from%20canisters.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20their%20co-accused%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20raised%20slogans%20outside%20Parliament%20and%20used%20coloured%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20people%20were%20arrested%20soon%20after%20and%20charged%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%20Over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20and%20Lalit%20Jha%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20have%20said%20their%20objective%20