eared%20Dead%20Off%20Libya%20Coast%20After%20Boat%20Sinks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2061%20migrants%20were%20missing%20and%20presumed%20dead%20after%20their%20boat%20sank%20off%20Libya's%20coast%2C%20the%20International%20Organization%20for%20Migration%20(IOM)%20said%20Saturday%2C%20in%20the%20latest%20such%20tragedy%20off%20North%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20migrants%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20died%20because%20of%20high%20waves%20which%20swamped%20their%20vessel%20after%20it%20left%20from%20Zuwara%2C%20on%20Libya's%20northwest%20coast%2C%20the%20IOM's%20Libya%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20survivors%2C%20it%20said%20there%20were%20approximately%2086%20migrants%20aboard%20--%20including%20women%20and%20children%20--%20from%20Nigeria%2C%20the%20Gambia%20and%20other%20African%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20people%20were%20rescued%20and%20transferred%20to%20a%20Libyan%20detention%20centre%2C%20said%20the%20IOM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20survivors%20were%20all%20in%20good%20condition%20and%20had%20received%20medical%20support%20from%20IOM%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibya%20and%20Tunisia%20are%20principal%20departure%20points%20for%20migrants%20risking%20dangerous%20sea%20voyages%20in%20hopes%20of%20reaching%20Europe%2C%20via%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20153%2C000%20migrants%20arrived%20in%20Italy%20this%20year%20from%20Tunisia%20and%20Libya%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20refugee%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItaly's%20far-right%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20won%20elections%20last%20year%20after%20vowing%20to%20stop%20illegal%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeloni's%20hard-right%20government%20has%20so%20far%20taken%20numerous%20measures%20to%20restrict%20the%20activities%20of%20charity%20ships%20that%20save%20people%20attempting%20the%20perilous%20crossing%20from%20North%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20approach%20to%20tackling%20illegal%20migration%20won%20praise%20from%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20Rome%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20vowed%20to%20stop%20migrant%20boat%20landings%20on%20their%20countries'%20shores%20and%20to%20step%20up%20efforts%20to%20combat%20people%20smugglers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20has%20described%20the%20central%20Mediterranean%20migration%20route%20as%20the%20world's%20deadliest%2C%20claiming%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlavio%20Di%20Giacomo%2C%20an%20IOM%20spokesperson%2C%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20on%20Saturday%20that%20more%20than%202%2C250%20people%20died%20this%20year%20on%20the%20central%20Mediterranean%20migrant%20route%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bdramatic%20figure%20which%20demonstrates%20that%20unfortunately%20not%20enough%20is%20being%20done%20to%20save%20lives%20at%20sea%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adriana%2C%20a%20fishing%20boat%20loaded%20with%20750%20people%20en%20route%20from%20Libya%20to%20Italy%2C%20went%20down%20in%20international%20waters%20off%20southwest%20Greece%20on%20June%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20survivors%2C%20the%20ship%20was%20carrying%20mainly%20Syrians%2C%20Pakistanis%20and%20Egyptians.%20Only%20104%20survived%20and%2082%20bodies%20were%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Libya%2C%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20violence%20since%20the%20overthrow%20and%20killing%20of%20dictator%20Moamer%20Kadhafi%20in%20a%20NATO-backed%20uprising%20helped%20turn%20the%20country%20into%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20human%20traffickers%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20abuses%20ranging%20from%20extortion%20to%20slavery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702790520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F3dbn4