ng%20up%20property%20prices%20by%20as%20much%20as%20thrice%20the%20original%20price%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20authorities%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20anticipated%20surge%20in%20visitors%20for%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20stepping%20up%20security%20measures%20and%20making%20logistical%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20experience%20for%20the%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20cameras%20have%20been%20installed%20across%20the%20town%20and%20drones%20will%20be%20used%20to%20review%20the%20security%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20about%204%2C000%20saints%20are%20expected%20for%20the%20mega%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20Trust%20Secretary%2C%20however%2C%20has%20asked%20people%20to%20celebrate%20the%20event%20by%20visiting%20local%20temples%20in%20their%20cities%20and%20towns%20to%20avoid%20overcrowding%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20Assemble%20at%20the%20temple%20nearest%20to%20you%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20its%20small%20or%20big.%20Go%20to%20the%20temple%20which%20is%20feasible%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Champat%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20guarantee%20a%20feast%20for%20the%20devotees%2C%20but%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20they%20get%20basic%20meals%20and%20a%20place%20to%20sleep%2C%20if%20not%20air-conditioned%20rooms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20is%20ready%2C%20so%20is%20the%20idol%2C%20but%20it%20could%20take%20another%20two%20years%20for%20the%20entire%20temple%20to%20be%20constructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVedic%20rituals%20for%20the%20Pran-Pratishtha%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20on%20January%2016%2C%20a%20week%20before%20the%20main%20ceremony.%20The%20main%20rituals%20at%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20wil