ic%20nudity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20rule%20change%20came%20after%20AI-generated%20women%20began%20streaming%20topless%20on%20the%20site.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwitch%20cited%20the%20ability%20of%20AI%20to%20create%20realistic%20nude%20images%20for%20the%20reversal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETwitch%20is%20rolling%20back%20its%20new%20rules%20allowing%20%26quot%3Bartistic%20nudity%26quot%3B%20just%20two%20days%20after%20updating%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitch-porn-streaming-moderation-problem-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esexual%20content%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwitch%20CEO%20Dan%20Clancy%20announced%20the%20change%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsafety.twitch.tv%2Fs%2Farticle%2FSexual-Content-Policy-Update%3Flanguage%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20realized%20the%20rule%20went%20%26quot%3Btoo%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20AI%20can%20create%20realistic%20images%20that%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20distinguish%20between%20digital%20art%20and%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20wish%20we%20would%20have%20predicted%20this%20outcome%2C%20part%20of%20our%20job%20is%20to%20make%20adjustments%20that%20serve%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Clancy%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%20%26quot%3BI%20apologize%20for%20the%20confusion%20that%20this%20update%20has%20caused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20update%20to%20Twitch's%20sexual%20content%20policy%20followed%20a%20new%20trend%20in%20which%20some%20women%20streaming%20on%20the%20platform%20used%20certain%20camera%20angles%20to%20appear%20topless%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkotaku.com%2Ftwitch-nudity-sexual-content-update-rules-changes-1851102825%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKotaku%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F12%2F15%2F2400