proval%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%2C%20we%20see%20no%20reason%20to%20entertain%20this%20writ%20petition%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20her%20petition%20and%20alleged%20that%20her%20plea%20was%20dismissed%20in%20eight%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9D%20I%20thought%20that%20the%20highest%20court%20will%20definitely%20hear%20such%20a%20straight%20forward%20benign%20prayer.%20What%20did%20I%20know%3F%20My%20writ%20petition%20was%20dismissed%20in%208%20seconds%20without%20any%20hearing%20and%20consideration%20of%20my%20prayers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20the%20open%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20judge%20expressed%20her%20scepticism%20about%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20in%20her%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20Justice%20will%20I%20give%20to%20others%20when%20I%20am%20myself%20hopeless%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20her%20letter%2C%20the%20judge%20also%20issued%20a%20message%20to%20working%20women%20in%20the%20country%2C%20warning%20them%20of%20the%20tall%20order%20of%20their%20fight%20against%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20tell%20all%20the%20working%20women%20in%20India%3A%20Learn%20to%20live%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20truth%20of%20our%20lives.%20The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers%E2%80%A6.And%20I%20am%20judge.%20I%20could%20not%20even%20a%20muster%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20for%20myself%2C%20let%20alone%20justice.%20I%20advise%20all%20women%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20a%20toy%2C%20or%20a%20non-living%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702724067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter