Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20was%20told%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20that%20it%20has%20identified%20the%20places%20of%20worship%20that%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20during%20the%20clashes.%20The%20bench%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20list%20of%20these%20places%20to%20the%20committee%20within%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20all%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20denomination%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20such%20structures%2C%20which%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20should%20be%20identified%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20was%20also%20permitted%20by%20the%20court%20to%20prepare%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20proposal%2C%20including%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20places%20of%20worship%20which%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%E2%80%9D%20and%20extended%20its%20term%20by%20six%20months%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuzefa%20Ahmadi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Meitei%20Christian%20Churches%20Council%2C%20said%20the%20court%20should%20direct%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20make%20arrangements%20so%20that%20Christians%20can%20congregate%20for%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibha%20Datta%20Makhija%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20committee%2C%20said%20the%20panel%20%E2%80%9Chad%20visited%20and%20found%20that%20religious%20and%20non-religious%20buildings%20have%20suffered%20large%20degree%20of%20damage.%20Religious%20places%20were%20of%20various%20faiths%20including%20some%20Buddhist%20temples.%20Therefore%20we%20had%20asked%20the%20state%20to%20make%20a%20list%20of%20damaged%20places%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20assured%20by%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20and%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20will%20ensure%20that%20people%20in%20relief%20camps%20can%20participate%20in%20Christmas%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702718044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Finform-panel-of-steps-to-secure-places-of-worship-supreme-court-tells-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Details%20of%20all%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20denomination%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20such%20structures%2C%20which%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20should%20be%20identified%2C%20the%20court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Finform-panel-of-steps-to-secure-places-of-worship-supreme-court-tells-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coral%20islands%20in%20Australia%20at%20risk%20of%20disappearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702716039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FBF50%2Fproduction%2F_132067984_fec0240ad25f559d9879a9f4b6befc8cf79f1f170_0_4004_26691000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67735681%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20disappearance%20of%20the%20islands%20could%20affect%20Australia's%20maritime%20borders%2C%20a%20study%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67735681%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67735681.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67735681.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Schindler%E2%80%99s%20List'%20at%2030%3A%20A%20Look%20Back%20at%20Steven%20Spielberg%E2%80%99s%20Shattering%20Mas