e%20I%20started%20Infinity%20Inc.%20in%20February%202018%2C%20our%20priority%20was%20to%20sign%20Moko%20as%20an%20artist.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20appreciated%20that%20his%20art%20stems%20from%20his%20love%20of%20his%20culture%20and%20people%20and%20is%20marked%20by%20originality%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20artists%20these%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moko%20remembers%20the%20call%20he%20received%20from%20Asalie%20following%20his%20post-graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20call%2C%20Assalie%20told%20me%20how%20they%20wanted%20to%20sign%20me%20as%20an%20artist.%20Without%20any%20second%20thoughts%2C%20I%20signed%20with%20them%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20music.%20Joining%20Infinity%20Inc.%20gave%20me%20access%20to%20a%20professional%20studio%20with%20in-house%20producers%20and%20sound%20engineers%20who%20would%20help%20me%20make%20the%20music%20I%20wanted.%20From%20struggling%20early%20on%20to%20put%20out%20music%20and%20asking%20my%20mother%20for%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20studio%20session%2C%20today%20I%20have%20access%20to%20the%20tools%20I%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvincing%20his%20parents%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20hard.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20am%20going%20with%20music%20full-time%20and%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240763%2Fnagaland-shiitake-oyster-mushrooms-earns-lakhs-how-to-grow-spores-method-scientist-innovation-agritech-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimapur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%20that%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20make%20my%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jp