%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFish%20farming%20did%20not%20prove%20profitable%20for%20us%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20input%20costs.%20If%20we%20sold%20a%20fish%20for%20Rs%20100%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2080.%20We%20were%20only%20left%20with%20Rs%2020%20profit.%20It%20was%20very%20little%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sanjay%20came%20across%20a%20news%20report%20that%20mentioned%20the%20profitability%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming.%20Motivated%20to%20try%20his%20hands%20in%20cultivating%20oysters%2C%20he%20bought%2025%2C000%20oysters%20to%20cultivate%20in%20his%20water%20bank.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20roped%20in%20other%20farmer%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20collective%20investment%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20the%20group%20started%20oyster%20farming.%20And%20in%20a%20year%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89574%2Fsanjay-gandate-pearl-farmer-gadchiroli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerate%20an%20income%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-300x157.jpg