%20simple%20yet%20risky%20as%20stitching%20a%20wound%20with%20a%20beating%20heart%20underneath%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20initially%20developed%20SSI%20Mantra%2C%20but%20after%20a%20while%2C%20he%20launched%20an%20enhanced%20version%20called%20SSI%20Mantra%202.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20system%20was%20to%20make%20it%20user-friendly%2C%20ergonomic%2C%20and%20with%20more%20features%20%E2%80%94%20both%20for%20the%20surgeons%20as%20well%20as%20for%20the%20table-side%20assisting%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20designed%20is%20called%20an%20open-face%20console%2C%20featuring%20a%20large%2032-inch%204K%20high-definition%20resolution%203D%20monitor.%20This%20design%20enhances%20magnification%2C%20providing%20surgeons%20with%20the%20capability%20to%20perform%20procedures%20with%20exceptional%20precision.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20remarkable%20advancement%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20says%20they%20have%20integrated%20safety%20features%20with%20a%20head-tracking%20camera.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20surgeon%20wears%20glasses%20with%20specific%20markers%20that%20are%20tracked%20by%20the%20camera.%20This%20ensures%20that%20if%20the%20surgeon%20looks%20away%20from%20the%20monitor%2C%20even%20while%20moving%20their%20hands%2C%20the%20system%20will%20not%20respond.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20safety%20measure%20that%20requires%20the%20camera%20view%20to%20be%20within%20sight%20for%20operation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20also%20has%20a%2023-inch%20large%20monitor%20with%20all%20controls%20easily%20accessible%20to%20the%20surgeon.%20This%20allows%20the%20surgeon%20to%20retrieve%20any%20of%20the%20DICOM%20images%20from%20the%20server%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20radiology%20department%20or%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20display%20them%20conveniently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20team%20has%20developed%20proprietary%